<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">Dear <%= @freelancer.name %>,</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  You have successfully submitted changes for the task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>."
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;"><strong>Task Details:</strong></p>
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Task ID:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.id %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Title:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Deadline:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.deadline ? @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : "Not set" %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Status:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.status.capitalize %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  The client (<strong><%= @task.client.name %></strong>) has been notified of your submitted changes. Should any additional revisions be required, the client will communicate with you directly via GigHive.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  You can view the task details and monitor the client's feedback here:
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <%= link_to 'View Task on GigHive', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007BFF; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;' %>
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Thank you for your dedication and professionalism. Keep up the great work!
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Sincerely,<br>
  The GigHive Team
</p>